{% block content %}
<section class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <img class="mx-auto d-block img-fluid" src="/static/images/stanford_dragon_jade.png" width="800px"/>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <h6 class="mx-auto"><small>The Standford Dragon with a jade-like medium. Rendered with my hobby renderer, Lantern.</small></h6>
    </div>
    <div class="row pt-5">
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <p class="lead">
                Hello. My name is Adrian Astley. I'm a Tools and Infrastructure Engineer at Activision Central Technology. I create and maintain software tools for the studios making Call of Duty.
