            </p>
            <p class="lead">
                Within programming, my areas of interest are tools design and implementation, 3D graphics, and path tracing. Outside of programming, I'm a board game nerd and rock climbing enthusiast.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-1"></div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img class="mx-auto d-block img-fluid" src="/static/images/headshot.png" width="300px"/>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
